snippet.title: Wo Long: Fallen Dynasty - Story Trailer
snippet.description:
Confront countless demons, famous warlords and a conspiracy surrounding an elixir that promises immortality in Wo Long: Fallen Dynasty.

Release date - 3/3/2023. 
Pre-orders available now for Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5 and Steam. Available day one on Xbox Game Pass.

Game Details - https://teamninja-studio.com/wolong/
